As a result, some fruits may develop dry skin, wrinkles, scars, black spots, or water cracks. These are completely normal and do not affect the flesh inside. In fact, dragon fruit that has endured natural elements like wind, sun, and rain tends to be even sweeter and juicier.
Wrinkled Skin
Cracks, Scars
